  abstract = {This paper presents the official ranking and benchmarking results of the QU-BraTS 2023 challenge. Fourteen teams submitted uncertainty-aware segmentation methods. Metrics include RMSD and correlation between uncertainty and error. Ensemble methods achieved RMSD ~0.059 and CORR 0.64. The analysis highlights calibration gaps and establishes a new benchmark for clinical-grade uncertainty quantification.},
